    "2865:28": "none“> evamubhayayogināṃ dviprakāreṇa hṛdayasaṃcodanamabhidhāyedanīṃ",
    "2865:29": "vikalpitaniṣpataniṣpannayogināṃ prthamapaṭaloktadvividhadevatārupoddayotanārthamekādaśamapaṭalamupakṣipannāha|",
    "2865:30": "athetyādi|sarvatathāgatavajraṃ praṇavādyakṣaratrayaṃ tenotpadyamānā puruṣottamā",
    "2865:31": "devatā yasmin samādhau tannāmakaṃ samādhi citaikāgratāṃ samāpadyāmukhīkṛtya",
    "2865:32": "idamudājahāra |",
    "2865:33": "kiṃ tat ? sarvatathāgatānāṃ mantrāḥ guhyābhūtā",
    "2865:34": "vajravidyā sarvatathāgatamantravajravidyā oṅkārāditritayameva|",
    "2865:35": "tairniṣpādyate",
    "2865:36": "paruṣadevatā yasmin tatpaṭalamuktavāniti saṅgitikāraḥ amu mevārtha",
    "2865:37": "bhagavadvacanena darśayannāha|",
