    "2865:44": "none“> trivajrāḥ kāyavākcittavajrāḥ tanniṣpādakānyakṣarāṇi",
    "2865:45": "oṅkārādīni trivajrākṣarāṇi tāni mantrāgrāṇi sarvamantraprabhāvatvāt |",
    "2865:46": "tairmahāmudrāvibhāvanaṃ kartavyam |",
    "2865:47": "mahāmudreti bhūrbhuvaḥ svaḥ",
    "2865:48": "prapūjyatvānmahartī mudaṃ harṣa dravati gacchatīti mahāmudrā |",
    "2865:49": "tasyā vibhāvanaṃ",
    "2865:50": "kartavyayanuṣṭhe yam |",
    "2865:51": "jñānavajreṇa sadhakena sarvabodhiḥ pañcākārābhisaṃbodhiḥ",
    "2865:52": "tatsamāvaham |",
