    "2865:58": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2865:59": "none“> oṅkāramityādinā akṣaratrayasya kāritraṃ",
    "2865:60": "darśayati | oṅkāraṃ tathāgatahṛdayaṃ tad yogino'bhedyakāyanivartakatvāt",
    "2865:61": "vajrakayasamāvaham |",
    "2865:62": "bodhistathatā |",
    "2865:63": "tato nirmito niṣpanna ātmā yasya sa",
    "2865:64": "bodhirnirātmā amitabhaḥ |",
    "2865:65": "tasya bhāvo nairātmyam |",
    "2865:66": "nairātmyamāḥkarāṃ tatsvabhāvaṃ",
    "2865:67": "yogino'bhedyavāṅnivartakatvāt vagvajrasamāvaham |",
    "2865:68": "kāyavācorāśrayabhūtaṃ cittaṃ",
    "2865:69": "kāyavākcittam akṣobhyasvabhāvam |",
    "2865:70": "trivajrāṇāmabhedyabhinnatvaṃ yasmin tat",
    "2865:71": "trivajrābhedyaṃ cittaṃ tadyogisantāne niṣpādayatīti trivajrābhedyasamāvahaṃ hūṃkāramityevamāha",
    "2865:72": "sarvatathāgatakāya vākcittamantrapuruṣo mahāvajradharaḥ|",
