    "2865:79": "none“> anantaroktamahāmudrāniṣpatti ( ttai )",
    "2865:80": "rānupūvrya darśayannāha |",
    "2865:81": "khavajretyādi |",
    "2865:82": "khavajramakāśaṃ madhyaṃ tadgataṃ sarvavajrajaṃ maṇḍalaṃ cintayet |",
    "2865:83": "sarvavajrāṇi",
    "2865:84": "locanādicaturdevyaḥ tābhiranupūvryeṇa nirvartitaṃ maṇḍalaṃ bhavayet | tatra",
    "2865:85": "bhūbhāgopari bhrūṃkāraṃ kūṭāgāraniṣpattihetu bhūtaṃ vajrameghāstathāgatasamūhāḥ|",
    "2865:86": "teṣāmadhimokṣeṇa yathāsthanaṃ spharaṇaṃ tadāvahayati dhārayatīti",
    "2865:87": "vajrameghaspharāvahaṃ bhrūṃkāram|",
    "2865:88": "tatretyādinā bhruṃkarapradarśanaṃ vajramaṇḍalaṃ",
    "2865:89": "sūryamaṇḍalaṃ tanmadhyasthaṃ hūṃkāraṃ prabhāvayet|",
    "2865:90": "hūṃkāraniṣpannaṃ sūryamaṇḍalaṃ",
    "2865:91": "bhāvayedityabhiprāyaḥ|",
    "2865:92": "normal;mso-pagination:",
