    "2865:98": "none“> tathaivoṃkārāḥkāraniṣpannaṃ candrapadhmamaṇḍalaṃ",
    "2865:99": "bhāvayet| evaṃ maṇḍalatrayaṃ niṣpādya padhmakarṇikopari tadeva bījatrayaṃ",
    "2865:100": "vinyasedityāmnāyaḥ|",
    "2865:101": "bhrūṃkārmālayamityādinā pūrvoktamartha nigamayati|",
    "2865:102": "ādhāramaṇḍalaṃ",
    "2865:103": "dhyātvainaṃ cihnatrayaṃ bhāvayet|",
    "2865:104": "nānyatheti|",
