    "2865:111": "none“> hṛdayamityādi|",
    "2865:112": "tryadhvabuddhebhyaḥ",
    "2865:113": "tryadhvatathāgatānāṃ tryadhvabuddhānāmiti prāptatvāt|",
    "2865:114": "hṛdayaṃ candramaṇḍalaṃ",
    "2865:115": "cittasaṃketitatvāt|",
    "2865:116": "kāyavākcitaṃ tryakṣaraṃ tena yasmin racyate sthivate tat",
    "2865:117": "kāyavākcittarañjanaṃ candrabimbaṃ cihnatrayamupamardyatāṃ bhavayet| tataḥ",
    "2865:118": "kimityāha omityādi|",
    "2865:119": "tasmiścandramaṇḍale buddhakāyasaṃjñakamoṅkāraṃ tathā",
    "2865:120": "buddhavākpathamāḥkāram|",
    "2865:121": "normal;mso-pagination:",
