    "2865:162": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2865:163": "none“> sarvatathāgatetyādinā anumevārthamupasaṃharati|",
    "2865:164": "sarvatathāgatakāyavākicattatryakṣaraṃ tasya samayaṃ tadudbhūtaṃ sūryādimaṇḍalatritayam|",
    "2865:165": "tasmin tattvaṃ padyopari tryakṣaram|",
    "2865:166": "jñānamiti sarva parāvṛttiniṣpannaṃcandramaṇḍalam",
    "2865:167": "vajraṃ candramaṇḍalopari vinyastākṣaratritayanivṛttaṃ pañcasūcikamahāvajram",
    "2865:168": "tenādhiṣṭhiyate niṣpādyata ityadhiṣṭhānaṃ mahāmudrārupam tasya hetuḥ kāraṇam |",
    "2865:169": "tanniṣpādikā cittaikāgratā samādhiḥ sa tathoktaḥ |",
    "2865:170": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2865:171": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2865:172": "none;text-autospace:none“>",
    "2865:173": "normal;mso-pagination:",
