    "2865:175": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2865:176": "none“> vivikteṣvityādinā sādhakasya pratipatti",
    "2865:177": "darśayati | vivikteṣu janasampātarahiteṣu ramyeṣviti puṣpaphalapallavopetavividhatarulatopagūdamanojñasalilāśayavirajitamanonukūleṣu",
    "2865:178": "sthāneṣu sthitvā yaḥ sādhakaḥ imamanantarokttaṃ yogaṃ samārabhedabhyaset ,",
    "2865:179": "tena kāyavākcittaṃ mahāvajradharatvaṃ sidhyate",
    "2865:180": "sādhyate | pakṣaikeneti pakṣaḥ gurudevatāviṣaye sampratyayaḥ|",
    "2865:181": "tasminnekena",
    "2865:182": "niścitena tatpareṇa na saṃśayaḥ|",
    "2865:183": "niyataṃ kāyavākcittaṃ sādhyate'nena krameṇotpatti",
    "2865:184": "kramamabhyasan mantrī niṣpannakramasamādhimadhigamya niyatamihaiva janmani",
    "2865:185": "mahāvajradharatvaṃ prāpnotītyabhiprāyaḥ |",
